originalText.text: She is exceptional. She takes her time with her patients. Calls back and follows up. She explains things in a way you could understand...low on jargon and medical terms. She has empathy and is very knowledgeable. She leaves no rock unturned and gives you a complete checkup. She is very accessable thru video chat or visits. Her bedside manner is unmatched.

originalText.text: Acabo de leer las opiniones y estoy de acuerdo con todas las opiniones que son positivas. Muy profesional, le dio seguimiento a mi caso y a pocos días me llamó y me dejó un mensaje que ya tenían mis resultados de los exámenes. Además, de la farmacia me llamaron para que recogiera la medicina recomendada por Joanne y otra medicina que necesitaba para tratar una infección que recuerdo haber mencionado en mi primera consulta. Mi opinión siempre será positiva para profesionales de la medicina, que buscan las mejores formas que están a su alcance para ayudar a sus pacientes en necesidad. ¡Excelente servicio!

text.text: I just read the opinions and I agree with all the opinions that are positive. Very professional, he followed up on my case and a few days later he called me and left me a message that they already had my test results. Additionally, the pharmacy called me to pick up the medicine Joanne recommended and another medicine I needed to treat an infection that I remember mentioning in my first consultation. My opinion will always be positive for medical professionals, who look for the best ways within their reach to help their patients in need. Excellent service!
